highlights.text: “อะไรฉันก็ยอม” by Saran, Pondering, WHALJAY, and SLOWVXNZ is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 58 spots at #134.
“เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1260 days straight.
Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #27.
“รักคนมีเจ้าของ” by Ai Nam is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #187.
